item.description:
This event is listed for the hikers who will be hiking the Bonds and staying overnight in Twin Mountain.

Since we need to spot some cars at the end of the long hike, some of us are meeting to set up the shuttle in the Lincoln Woods trail parking lot, and then heading to dinner-probably the Woodstock Station.

RSVP here if you are in this overnight group so we can watch for you- it should be a fun evening before a great hike.

If your in the neighborhood and would like to just join us for dinner, let us know!
item.name: Bonds Lincoln Woods Carspot and Dinner
